===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|coypus|pl2=coypu}}

#A large, [[crepuscular]], [[semiaquatic]] [[rodent]] (''Myocastor coypus'') resembling a large [[rat]], having bright [[orange]]-[[yellow]] [[incisor]]s, native to [[South America]], [[Europe]], [[Asia]] and [[North America]], valued for its fur in eastern Europe and central Asia and considered a pest elsewhere.

====Synonyms====
*[[nutria]] (''especially North America'')

